{
  "texts": [
    "In the initial phase, papers were filtered based on their titles and abstracts.",
    "Subsequently, in a further round of evaluation, papers were excluded if they lacked clarity in presenting model results or failed to present the included DL architecture clearly.",
    "Following the PRISMA (Preferred Reporting Items for Systematic Reviews and Meta-Analyses) guidelines, an initial collection of 213 papers were gathered based on the comprehensive search strategy.",
    "Duplicate papers, collected from various digital libraries, were removed, resulting in 145 unique studies.",
    "During the next stage, 52 papers were excluded after title and abstract screening due to irrelevance to our scope of review."
  ]
}